name: staring at the camera
description:
The owner of this token is entitled to one video call with the artist, not to be fewer than 30 minutes long, during which the artist will stare at the camera.

Once the call has taken place, this token will be deemed to have been "redeemed" and a call will not be available to future owners. Redemption status will be available at https://jeremy.org/nft/staring.html until at least the end of the 2027 calendar year.
